    <title>1. Laravel Practice</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/10/27/1-Laravel-Practice/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/10/27/1-Laravel-Practice/</id>
    <published>2019-10-26T16:08:28.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-10-26T16:16:33.457Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-Laravel-Practice"><a href="#1-Laravel-Practice" class="headerlink" title="1. Laravel Practice"></a>1. Laravel Practice</h1><hr><h2 id="Installation"><a href="#Installation" class="headerlink" title="Installation"></a>Installation</h2><ol><li>Install in docker (using richarvey now , should create by myself)</li></ol><ul><li>透過 <code>composer global require laravel/installer</code>去安裝</li><li>會面臨到 <code>bash : laravel command not found</code> 的問題，透過 <code>export PATH=&quot;~/.composer/vendor/bin:$PATH&quot;</code> 去解決</li><li>接著， <code>laravel new project</code> (記得要加-f )</li><li>然後記得去改 <code>vi /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/*</code></li><li><code>/project/public</code></li><li>以上是以 nginx 環境</li></ul><h2 id="DB-setting"><a href="#DB-setting" class="headerlink" title="DB setting"></a>DB setting</h2><ol><li>via <code>php artisan make:auth</code> create 登入畫面</li><li>via <code>php artisan migrate</code> create DB structure，根據 <code>database/migrations/2014_10_12_000000_create_users_table.php</code> 去部署 DB structure</li></ol><h2 id="Eloquent"><a href="#Eloquent" class="headerlink" title="Eloquent"></a>Eloquent</h2><ul><li><p>Eloquent is laravel ORM<br><code>php artisan make:model Article</code> Artisan 幫我們生成的Model 文件</p></li><li><p>Eloquent讓一個<b>Model</b>對應一張數據庫表，並且在底層封裝了很多<b>function</b>，可以讓Model非常方便地調用</p></li><li><p>只需要繼承Eloquent，就可以 use <b>first() find() where() orderBy()</b> 等事情</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Article</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> \<span class="title">Eloquent</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">protected</span> $fillable = [];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="基礎使用要點"><a href="#基礎使用要點" class="headerlink" title="基礎使用要點"></a>基礎使用要點</h4></li></ul><ol><li><p>每一個繼承Eloquent 的類都有兩個’固定用法’<br><code>Article::find($number)</code> <code>Article::all()</code><br>前者會得到一個帶有DB中取出來值的對象，後者會得到一個包含整個DB的對象合集。</p></li><li><p>所有的中間方法如<code>where()</code> <code>orderBy()</code> 等都能夠同時支持’靜態’ 和’非靜態式’ 兩種方式調用<br>即<code>Article::where()...</code>  和 <code>Article::....-&gt;where()</code>。</p></li><li><p>所有的’非固定用法’ 的調用最後都需要一個操作來’收尾’，本片教程中有兩個’收尾操作’：<code>-&gt;get()</code> 和<code>-&gt;first()</code>。</p></li><li><p>如果你不理解為什麼’Article’這個類可以使用<code>-&gt;where()</code> <code>-&gt;get()</code>等很多方法的話，說明你需要去讀一下PHP對象繼承的文檔了：對象繼承。</p></li></ol><h4 id="model-DB-manipulation"><a href="#model-DB-manipulation" class="headerlink" title="model DB manipulation"></a>model DB manipulation</h4><h6 id="Example"><a href="#Example" class="headerlink" title="Example"></a>Example</h6><ol><li>Find the article which id = 2 and print it out<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$article  =  Article :: find( <span class="number">2</span> );</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span>  $article -&gt; title ;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>Search and find the title which is “我是標題”，and print id<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$article  =  Article :: where( <span class="string">' title '</span> , <span class="string">'我是標題'</span> ) -&gt; first();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span>  $article -&gt; id ;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>Search all article and repeat to print all title<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$articles  =  Article :: all(); <span class="comment">//此處得到的$articles是一個對象集合，可以在後面加上'-&gt;toArray()'變成多維數組。</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">foreach</span> ( $articles  <span class="keyword">as</span>  $article ) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">echo</span>  $article -&gt; title ;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>Search all the article which id is between 10~20 and print all the title out</li></ol><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$articles  =  Article :: where( <span class="string">' id '</span> , <span class="string">' &gt; '</span> , <span class="number">10</span> ) -&gt; where( <span class="string">' id '</span> , <span class="string">' &lt; '</span> , <span class="number">20</span> ) -&gt; get();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">foreach</span> ( $articles  <span class="keyword">as</span>  $article ) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">echo</span>  $article -&gt; title ;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="9"><li>Search all the article and repeat to print all the title ,按照updated_at 倒序排序</li></ol><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$articles  =  Article :: where( <span class="string">' id '</span> , <span class="string">' &gt; '</span> , <span class="number">10</span> ) -&gt; where( <span class="string">' id '</span> , <span class="string">' &lt; '</span> , <span class="number">20</span> ) -&gt; orderBy( <span class="string">' updated_at '</span> , <span class="string">' desc '</span> ) -&gt; get();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">foreach</span> ( $articles  <span class="keyword">as</span>  $article ) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">echo</span>  $article -&gt; title ;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="使用Migration-和Seeder"><a href="#使用Migration-和Seeder" class="headerlink" title="使用Migration 和Seeder"></a>使用Migration 和Seeder</h2><h4 id="Use-artisan-生成-Migration"><a href="#Use-artisan-生成-Migration" class="headerlink" title="Use artisan 生成 Migration"></a>Use artisan 生成 Migration</h4><ul><li><p><code>php artisan make:migration create_articles_table</code></p></li><li><p>A file which name is 2*****_create_articles_table has been create successfully。<br>We edit its “up” function:</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>  <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>  <span class="title">up</span> <span class="params">()</span> </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123; </span><br><span class="line">    Schema::create(<span class="string">'articles'</span> , <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="params">( Blueprint $table )</span>     </span>&#123; </span><br><span class="line">        $table -&gt; increments( <span class="string">'id'</span> ); </span><br><span class="line">        $table -&gt; string( <span class="string">'title'</span> ); </span><br><span class="line">        $table -&gt; text( <span class="string">'body'</span> ) -&gt; nullable(); </span><br><span class="line">        $table -&gt; integer( <span class="string">'user_id'</span> ); </span><br><span class="line">        $table -&gt;timestamps(); </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>And we make the php into real MySQL database:</p></li></ul><p><code>php artisan migrate</code></p><h4 id="Use-artisan-生成-model-and-migration"><a href="#Use-artisan-生成-model-and-migration" class="headerlink" title="Use artisan 生成 model and migration"></a>Use artisan 生成 model and migration</h4><p><code>php artisan make:model Post -m</code></p><ul><li>model本身是個類別，所以採「大駝峰」命名，且名稱最後不加s</li><li>資料表命名規則為：table名稱小寫，且補上s</li></ul><h4 id="Use-artisan-生成-Seeder"><a href="#Use-artisan-生成-Seeder" class="headerlink" title="Use artisan 生成 Seeder"></a>Use artisan 生成 Seeder</h4><ul><li><p><code>php artisan make:seeder ArticleSeeder</code></p></li><li><p>Edit its “run” function</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">run</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">DB::table(<span class="string">'articles'</span>) -&gt; delete();    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>($i = <span class="number">0</span> ; $i &lt; <span class="number">10</span> ; $i ++) &#123; </span><br><span class="line">    \App\Article::create([<span class="string">'title'</span>=&gt;<span class="string">'Title'</span>.$i,<span class="string">'body'</span>=&gt;<span class="string">'Body'</span>.$i,<span class="string">'user_id'</span>=&gt;<span class="number">1</span>,]);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>把ArticleSeeder註冊到系統內。修改DatabaseSeeder.php的 “run” function</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>  <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>  <span class="title">run</span> <span class="params">()</span> </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123; </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">$this</span> -&gt; call( ArticleSeeder::class ); </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>執行<code>php artisan db:seed</code></p></li><li><p>Refresh articles table，already have 10 rows of fake data</p><h6 id="tags-Laravel-Laravel-setting"><a href="#tags-Laravel-Laravel-setting" class="headerlink" title="tags: Laravel, Laravel setting"></a>tags: <code>Laravel</code>, <code>Laravel setting</code></h6></li></ul>]]></content>
    
